%N A394197 Number of squares reachable in n (but no fewer) leaps of an antelope (the fairy chess piece) on an infinite chessboard.
%C A394197 An antelope is a (3,4)-leaper.
%C A394197 Coordination sequence of the infinite antelope graph.
%H A394197 Paolo Xausa, <a href="/A394197/b394197.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000</a>
